Package: locuszoomr
Title: Gene Locus Plot with Gene Annotations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Myles",family = "Lewis",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "myles.lewis@qmul.ac.uk",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9365-5345")))
Description: Pure R implementation of 'LocusZoom' for plotting genetic data at 
    genomic loci accompanied by gene annotations. It uses the 'LDlink' API to query 
    linkage disequilibrium data from the 1000 Genomes Project.
